Enum ColorMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ColorMarker>
      • info.ronjenkins.slf4bukkit.ColorMarker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ColorMarker>, org.slf4j.Marker

    public enum ColorMarker
extends Enum<ColorMarker>
implements org.slf4j.Marker
    SLF4J markers that map to a subset of ChatColors. These markers never contain any references (other markers).
    Author:
    Ronald Jack Jenkins Jr.
